  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The city of Sentinel Point is in danger and needs a protector! Protect it in this superhero themed roguelike deckbuilder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spend time, not mana:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is turn based but every card costs time and you will have to wait for it to be ready - When a villain tries to punch, you better already be blocking. Weave in punches while they recover in a tactical battle where every turn matters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/4a386d516ebaceea368f584ebfb2362f.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=608 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/4a386d516ebaceea368f584ebfb2362f.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/4a386d516ebaceea368f584ebfb2362f.mp4?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each run unique:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run you can choose one or two Archetypes such as Martial, Magic or Science to make the hero you want. You can also add a Aspect which adds extra cards - maybe your Magic User is also a mutant who can shapeshift? Did your Scientist learn how to become a speedster? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain gear, training to modify cards, extra powers and even a sidekick over the course of a run to help you out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/247a88f70f370c0aab768da3a770fb4e.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=472 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/247a88f70f370c0aab768da3a770fb4e.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/247a88f70f370c0aab768da3a770fb4e.mp4?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful though, because every hero you can play as also has a villainous side and their own deck to battle against. Every run also has a dark power behind it lending them power - Will you find they are channelling the power of a dark god? Do they have a death ray swivelling in your direction? Battle them and find out!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/0179b3a8f4cdd898c59198409be1b965.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=701 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/0179b3a8f4cdd898c59198409be1b965.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Play your way:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full game will come with a powerful mod maker which will let you make new cards, events, acts and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/6e2347eb82bb83492a1c7f9965d41c9e.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/6e2347eb82bb83492a1c7f9965d41c9e.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/6e2347eb82bb83492a1c7f9965d41c9e.mp4?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The city of Sentinel Point is in danger and needs a protector! Protect it in this superhero themed roguelike deckbuilder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spend time, not mana:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is turn based but every card costs time and you will have to wait for it to be ready - When a villain tries to punch, you better already be blocking. Weave in punches while they recover in a tactical battle where every turn matters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/4a386d516ebaceea368f584ebfb2362f.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=608 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/4a386d516ebaceea368f584ebfb2362f.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/4a386d516ebaceea368f584ebfb2362f.mp4?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each run unique:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run you can choose one or two Archetypes such as Martial, Magic or Science to make the hero you want. You can also add a Aspect which adds extra cards - maybe your Magic User is also a mutant who can shapeshift? Did your Scientist learn how to become a speedster? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain gear, training to modify cards, extra powers and even a sidekick over the course of a run to help you out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/247a88f70f370c0aab768da3a770fb4e.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=472 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/247a88f70f370c0aab768da3a770fb4e.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/247a88f70f370c0aab768da3a770fb4e.mp4?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful though, because every hero you can play as also has a villainous side and their own deck to battle against. Every run also has a dark power behind it lending them power - Will you find they are channelling the power of a dark god? Do they have a death ray swivelling in your direction? Battle them and find out!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/0179b3a8f4cdd898c59198409be1b965.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=701 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/0179b3a8f4cdd898c59198409be1b965.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Play your way:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full game will come with a powerful mod maker which will let you make new cards, events, acts and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/6e2347eb82bb83492a1c7f9965d41c9e.poster.avif?t=1741462184\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/6e2347eb82bb83492a1c7f9965d41c9e.webm?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966810/extras/6e2347eb82bb83492a1c7f9965d41c9e.mp4?t=1741462184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
